Thérèse Dorny https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Th%C3%A9r%C3%A8se_Dorny 0 Thérèse Dorny was a French film and theatre actress born in Paris, France on 18 September 1891. She died in Saint-Tropez, Var, France on 14 March 1976. Thérèse_Dorny was a_French_film_and_theatre_actress born in Paris , France on 18_September_1891 .
